This sturdy wooden wagon is supported by four over-sized treadwheels, each of which contains a magical miniature elephant. The wagon can carry up to 6000 pounds of weight. It moves at a speed of 40 ft. for up to eight hours per day, but never between midnight and dawn. The wagon follows your simple verbal commands to start, stop, turn, etc.